of the delicacies in the past♪

16
00:01:20,770 --> 00:01:25,630
♪My great partner.
Let's march on together♪

17
00:01:26,170 --> 00:01:29,340
♪Afflictions in life♪

18
00:01:29,780 --> 00:01:34,420
♪Let me feel them all♪

19
00:01:34,660 --> 00:01:39,980
♪As long as I'm happy.
Then every day♪

20
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:44,390
♪Is a perfect day with love♪

21
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:17,160
[The Legend of TAOTIE]

22
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:20,080
[Episode 37]

23
00:02:25,190 --> 00:02:26,030
All my life,

24
00:02:27,670 --> 00:02:29,830
I was trying to get my father's love.

25
00:02:31,110 --> 00:02:32,440
I hated my mother.

26
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:36,240
But actually, I was deceived

27
00:02:36,830 --> 00:02:37,960
and misunderstood everything.

28
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,830
A woman loved me.

29
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:44,830
But I didn't love her.

30
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:48,440
And the woman I love

31
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,000
doesn't love me.

32
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:55,240
Now, Zhao Ai

33
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:57,520
has become the wise emperor.

34
00:02:59,520 --> 00:03:00,830
And he will forget me.

35
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:03,190
In the end,

36
00:03:04,830 --> 00:03:06,720
I'll be all alone.

37
00:03:13,320 --> 00:03:13,960
Zhao Ai.

38
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,190
Don't look back.

39
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,390
Keep your back straight.

40
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:25,670
Let's go!

41
00:04:23,830 --> 00:04:25,510
Miss Zhu, Cuiyan,

42
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:26,950
I miss you so much.

43
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,270
Yingtao?

44
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:29,830
Why are you back?

45
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,480
What about Mr. Chang?

46
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,320
Where is he?

47
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:32,830
He painted me out and left.

48
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,640
I don't know where he has gone.

49
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,790
Why didn't you stop him

50
00:04:35,790 --> 00:04:36,830
from leaving?

51
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:39,000
How could I stop Mr. Chang?

52
00:04:41,670 --> 00:04:42,550
Glad he's safe.

53
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:43,320
Let's get in.

54
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:47,790
Miss Zhu.

55
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,270
Cuiyan.

56
00:04:49,510 --> 00:04:50,790
Where have you been lately?

57
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,000
Tell me about it.

58
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:53,320
Cuiyan.

59
00:04:54,790 --> 00:04:55,830
Miss Zhu.

60
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,790
Miss Zhu, why do you ignore me?

61
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:01,830
Miss Zhu.

62
00:05:02,350 --> 00:05:02,880
Cuiyan.

63
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:03,950
Miss Zhu.

64
00:05:04,110 --> 00:05:04,510
Cui...

65
00:05:06,790 --> 00:05:07,510
Keep your voice down.

66
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,160
Cuiyan,

67
00:05:10,640 --> 00:05:11,320
you know what?

68
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:13,160
Today, I went to Market Dong

69
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:15,880
and heard His Majesty is
the reincarnation of the True Dragon.

70
00:05:16,230 --> 00:05:17,270
He's diligent and caring.

71
00:05:17,270 --> 00:05:18,270
He also fights fiercely.

72
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:20,200
A few days ago,

73
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:21,790
he went to the Garuda Pass.

74
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:24,070
He fought bravely,
defeated Bei Di troops,

75
00:05:24,510 --> 00:05:25,720
and recovered lost ground.

76
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:27,480
People also say

77
00:05:27,670 --> 00:05:29,480
Da Liang will be very peaceful.

78
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:30,670
Keep your voice down.

79
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:33,600
Miss Zhu just fell asleep.

80
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:36,950
Cuiyan,

81
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:40,640
what on earth happened

82
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,110
between Miss Zhu and Mr. Chang?

83
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,320
Don't ask.

84
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,720
Miss Zhu will be sad.

85
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:48,070
Let's get out.

86
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:07,790
It is confirmed.

87
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:10,790
Seven years ago, the Chang's Bakery
in Yangzhou was on fire.

88
00:06:11,200 --> 00:06:12,230
A dozen people died.

89
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:13,320
Their bodies were hard to identify.

90
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,830
Chang Qing and Chang Xiaoli

91
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:17,000
went missing overnight.

92
00:06:17,790 --> 00:06:18,270
By Lu Ying.

93
00:06:20,230 --> 00:06:21,600
What's wrong with Miss Zhu?

94
00:06:21,950 --> 00:06:22,760
You don't even know.

95
00:06:23,070 --> 00:06:23,830
How could I?

96
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:43,280
♪Here's a flower for you♪

97
00:06:44,090 --> 00:06:48,030
♪I don't know what to say
when we look at each other♪

98
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,480
Qing,

99
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,160
why do you sleep so late?

100
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,000
Get up.

101
00:06:56,070 --> 00:06:56,800
Go out and play with me.

102
00:06:56,800 --> 00:07:01,580
♪My obsession leads to my fate♪

103
00:07:02,540 --> 00:07:08,070
♪Destiny is confusing over the years♪

104
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:14,550
♪It feels bleak even with the light on♪

105
00:07:15,210 --> 00:07:18,370
♪I see the shadow
when I almost forget you♪

106
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,070
Miss Zhu,

107
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:21,160
who does it remind you of?

108
00:07:23,110 --> 00:07:25,230
You.

109
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:34,030
♪Although the memories of our love
bring us pain♪

110
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:40,610
♪All I ask for is to hold your hand
until the end of time♪

111
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:44,020
♪Selflessly♪

112
00:07:44,230 --> 00:07:44,760
There.

113
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:47,500
♪We taste the sorrows and joys♪

114
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:53,790
♪I'll never let you go
till death do us part♪

115
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:30,350
Here's the thing.

116
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,480
In the Inspection Department,

117
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,470
there's a dungeon for demons.

118
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,230
Every time we caught a demon

119
00:08:35,230 --> 00:08:36,590
that hurt people,

120
00:08:36,590 --> 00:08:37,710
we put it in the dungeon.

121
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,760
It's heavily guarded.

122
00:08:40,110 --> 00:08:41,280
Every day, archers

123
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,590
patrol regularly.

124
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,640
Nothing has ever gone wrong.

125
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,280
But yesterday...

126
00:08:47,350 --> 00:08:48,200
At the Zi hour,

127
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:51,080
when Yundun patrolled
for the last time,

128
00:08:52,350 --> 00:08:53,910
he found all the imprisoned demons

129
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:55,640
had disappeared.

130
00:08:55,640 --> 00:08:56,790
Disappeared?

131
00:08:56,910 --> 00:08:57,400
Yes.

132
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:00,470
Is anything left behind?

133
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:01,550
No.

134
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,350
But I suspect

135
00:09:04,110 --> 00:09:06,030
a strong demon did that.

136
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:09,200
How do you know a demon did that?

137
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:11,080
My Fire-Ice Arrow sensed

138
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:13,030
its strong smell.

139
00:09:14,110 --> 00:09:14,880
Are you saying

140
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,760
when you entered the dungeon,

141
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:19,200
your weapon responded?

142
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:19,760
Yes.

143
00:09:20,230 --> 00:09:21,280
I'm sure about that.

144
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:23,710
Every time a strong demon

145
00:09:23,710 --> 00:09:25,030
approaches it,

146
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,760
it gives me a warning.

147
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,640
Strong demon?

148
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,030
Is Bai Ze back?

149
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:36,000
Bai Ze is

150
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:37,670
the only strong demon

151
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:38,910
in the mortal world.

152
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:41,840
It makes sense.

153
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:44,880
I shot him with my arrow.

154
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:46,080
Now, he's back.

155
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:47,230
That's why

156
00:09:47,230 --> 00:09:48,790
my arrow reacted strongly.

157
00:09:51,030 --> 00:09:53,150
If Bai Ze released those demons,

158
00:09:54,110 --> 00:09:55,670
he must be up to something evil.

159
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:28,590
Be on alert

160
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,640
for random wildfires!

161
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,840
Be on alert

162
00:10:36,590 --> 00:10:38,320
for random wildfires!

163
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:52,880
Mr. Lu,

164
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:53,840
they're all dead.

165
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:54,710
And all these people

166
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:56,200
were killed by demons.

167
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:57,710
The man over there...

168
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,000
The bruises all over him

169
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,030
were caused by a bird demon.

170
00:11:00,150 --> 00:11:01,790
I guess the bird demon from our dungeon

171
00:11:01,910 --> 00:11:02,910
killed him.

172
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,640
So,

173
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:10,670
the demons that killed them

174
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,710
possibly came from the dungeon

175
00:11:12,710 --> 00:11:13,710
of our department.

176
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:21,030
Recently,

177
00:11:21,350 --> 00:11:22,030
near Wuxia,

178
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:23,960
a dozen cases happened
where demons killed people.

179
00:11:24,470 --> 00:11:25,080
It's confirmed

180
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:27,280
the escaped demons did that.

181
00:11:27,470 --> 00:11:28,710
Now, people in town are scared.

182
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:29,520
What happened?

183
00:11:29,710 --> 00:11:30,320
Let's go.

184
00:11:30,710 --> 00:11:32,230
We've searched outside the town.

185
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:34,440
Are you sure
you haven't found their den?

186
00:11:35,230 --> 00:11:36,000
Not yet.

187
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:37,150
But Mr. Lu has been

188
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:38,520
gathering archers from different places.

189
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:40,760
They'll go out of town
to hunt the demons.

190
00:11:43,030 --> 00:11:44,790
How can Bai Ze

191
00:11:44,790 --> 00:11:46,200
bewitch those demons?

192
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,280
In the Garuda Pass, I injured Bai Ze.

193
00:11:49,440 --> 00:11:50,880
He's supposed to be healing himself.

194
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:52,910
How does he get the power

195
00:11:53,550 --> 00:11:55,230
to control so many demons?

196
00:12:01,710 --> 00:12:02,520
Miss Zhu,

197
00:12:02,640 --> 00:12:03,790
we were away for a long time.

198
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,230
The dust is everywhere.

199
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:06,550
I'm exhausted.

200
00:12:12,590 --> 00:12:14,030
But it's weird.

201
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:16,710
There's no dust on this painting.

202
00:12:17,470 --> 00:12:19,440
Did Yingtao clean it?

203
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,840
Bai Ze's Supernatural Creatures.

204
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,080
Why does Bai Ze

205
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:51,200
suddenly have a human body?

206
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,200
Miss Zhu.

207
00:12:54,030 --> 00:12:55,030
Look at the painting.

208
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:58,080
The demon beasts are looming

209
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,710
as if they would come alive

210
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,400
and get out of the painting.

211
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:04,640
Oh no.

212
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:06,110
What's wrong?

213
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:07,230
I guess Bai Ze

214
00:13:07,230 --> 00:13:08,640
has a human body

215
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,840
by using other demons' power.

216
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,150
This painting is the key.

217
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:13,960
I can't let him

218
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,470
appear like that again.

219
00:13:15,590 --> 00:13:16,880
The painting is the key?

220
00:13:17,110 --> 00:13:18,760
Then, let's tear it up.

221
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,200
Go guard the door.

222
00:13:22,520 --> 00:13:23,280
I'll seal it.

223
00:14:01,550 --> 00:14:02,670
Miss Zhu, are you all right?

224
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:03,110
I'm fine.

225
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:12,910
Taotie.

226
00:14:13,350 --> 00:14:14,080
I didn't expect

227
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,640
to see you again so soon.

228
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:18,080
Bai Ze,

229
00:14:19,790 --> 00:14:21,470
it's indeed you who released the demons

230
00:14:21,470 --> 00:14:22,440
and let them attack humans.

231
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,110
You stop me from sealing this painting.

232
00:14:26,590 --> 00:14:28,280
It must be what you possess.

233
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,030
You don't know yet, huh?

234
00:14:34,470 --> 00:14:36,280
I couldn't get my body back

235
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:37,960
without you, Taotie.

236
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:40,790
The dishes you made

237
00:14:40,790 --> 00:14:41,910
got the mermaid,

238
00:14:42,520 --> 00:14:44,200
the White Tiger, and the Black Bee

239
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:46,030
back to this painting.

240
00:14:46,230 --> 00:14:47,670
So, this painting

241
00:14:47,790 --> 00:14:49,960
has gathered the power of demons.

242
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,230
Or how could I appear like this?

243
00:14:52,710 --> 00:14:53,320
Bai Ze!

244
00:14:54,670 --> 00:14:55,280
Miss Zhu.

245
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:55,960
Cuiyan.

246
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:11,790
Miss Zhu.

247
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:14,470
Cuiyan,

248
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:15,640
put it away.

249
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:33,000
Savior.

250
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:36,280
Savior, who injured you again?

251
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:37,680
Go away.

252
00:15:39,590 --> 00:15:41,390
Taotie did, of course.

253
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:42,830
Miss Zhu?

254
00:15:43,070 --> 00:15:44,190
How about her? Is she injured?

255
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,950
I'm just worried
about the Dragon's blood.

256
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:50,590
I fear...

257
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:53,680
Robe.

258
00:15:54,950 --> 00:15:56,560
Robe.

259
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:07,120
That's what happened.

260
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:09,440
Miss Zhu doesn't seem to wake up.

261
00:16:09,510 --> 00:16:10,830
We didn't have a choice

262
00:16:10,830 --> 00:16:12,240
but to invite you over, Mr. Lu.

263
00:16:12,710 --> 00:16:13,480
Yeah.

264
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:14,710
Mr. Lu, what do we do?

265
00:16:15,360 --> 00:16:17,040
We don't know where Mr. Chang is.

266
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,680
Don't worry too much.

267
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:20,270
I'll send my men

268
00:16:20,830 --> 00:16:21,950
to look for Mr. Chang.

269
00:16:22,560 --> 00:16:23,710
Your top priority

270
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,920
is to take care of Miss Zhu.

271
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:31,630
Miss Zhu.

272
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:33,950
Mr. Lu.

273
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:39,070
Mr. Lu,

274
00:16:39,630 --> 00:16:40,320
it's Bai Ze.

275
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:41,590
Bai Ze?

276
00:16:41,590 --> 00:16:43,510
He's really hiding near Wuxia.

277
00:16:43,880 --> 00:16:44,630
And recently,

278
00:16:44,950 --> 00:16:46,680
demons have been killing people.

279
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:48,480
Bai Ze must be behind all this.

280
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:50,440
Luckily, you injured him

281
00:16:50,800 --> 00:16:52,040
and bought us some time

282
00:16:52,040 --> 00:16:53,120
to track him.

283
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:55,830
He gathered the demons

284
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:57,270
and stole my painting.

285
00:16:57,630 --> 00:16:59,000
It must have something
to do with the Lotus Tower.

286
00:16:59,590 --> 00:17:00,590
I've sealed the painting.

287
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:01,830
For a time,

288
00:17:02,390 --> 00:17:03,920
he will be too weak

289
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:04,800
to come out.

290
00:17:06,150 --> 00:17:07,510
If you find him,

291
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:08,870
let me know immediately.

