00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:57,040
I'll see how you can win.

588
00:32:48,350 --> 00:32:49,040
Miss Zhu.

589
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:51,600
Miss Zhu.

590
00:32:54,470 --> 00:32:56,110
What's attracting your attention?

591
00:32:56,320 --> 00:32:57,350
I've been calling you.

592
00:32:58,960 --> 00:32:59,510
You have?

593
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:04,230
Are you watching Miss Xiaoli
do the accounting?

594
00:33:04,680 --> 00:33:06,320
Do you not trust her?

595
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:08,870
Don't be ridiculous.

596
00:33:10,960 --> 00:33:12,720
I just think when she pays attention,

597
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,350
she looks so much like her brother.

598
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:17,110
I wonder how Qing is doing.

599
00:33:17,990 --> 00:33:20,390
So, you miss Mr. Chang.

600
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,150
You're quite nagging.

601
00:33:25,630 --> 00:33:26,200
Cuiyan.

602
00:33:27,390 --> 00:33:28,080
Think about it.

603
00:33:28,840 --> 00:33:30,230
If I splash you

604
00:33:30,870 --> 00:33:31,720
with the tea,

605
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:33,750
what will happen?

606
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:34,800
I...

607
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:36,270
I'll go clean the house.

608
00:33:53,800 --> 00:33:54,440
Qing,

609
00:33:55,750 --> 00:33:57,680
I don't know when you'll forgive me.

610
00:33:58,680 --> 00:33:59,510
But don't worry.

611
00:34:00,440 --> 00:34:02,080
I'll take good care of your sister.

612
00:34:08,790 --> 00:34:09,470
Miss Zhu.

613
00:34:11,750 --> 00:34:12,440
Miss Zhu?

614
00:34:12,790 --> 00:34:13,470
Is that you?

615
00:34:19,990 --> 00:34:21,030
Miss Xiaoli?

616
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,310
Why is it you?

617
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:23,710
It was blowing really hard.

618
00:34:23,990 --> 00:34:25,840
I saw the window in Zhu's room

619
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,880
was blown open.

620
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:28,510
So, I got in to close it.

621
00:34:32,470 --> 00:34:36,470
This window is never open.

622
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:45,080
Cuiyan, Miss Xiaoli,

623
00:34:45,230 --> 00:34:45,880
time for dinner.

624
00:34:58,080 --> 00:34:59,680
The brine duck isn't too greasy.

625
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:01,990
It tastes a bit sweet.

626
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:03,990
Tasty, isn't it?

627
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:05,360
Try this.

628
00:35:06,680 --> 00:35:08,550
Miss Zhu is a great chef.

629
00:35:08,640 --> 00:35:10,680
She makes extraordinary dishes.

630
00:35:11,230 --> 00:35:11,990
These days,

631
00:35:12,230 --> 00:35:13,840
I've heard many diners

632
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,270
talk about Zhu's cooking skills.

633
00:35:15,470 --> 00:35:17,640
They mentioned many fancy dishes,

634
00:35:17,950 --> 00:35:20,120
especially the Bee Soup.

635
00:35:20,880 --> 00:35:22,640
It's said to be really tasty.

636
00:35:22,950 --> 00:35:23,550
What's more,

637
00:35:23,750 --> 00:35:25,990
it tastes crispy and pungent.

638
00:35:26,270 --> 00:35:28,270
I'm quite curious.

639
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:30,120
In this case,

640
00:35:30,310 --> 00:35:31,710
I can make it for you.

641
00:35:32,030 --> 00:35:33,120
Thank you, Zhu.

642
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:36,160
Luckily, when I met Yuan
at the frontier,

643
00:35:36,160 --> 00:35:37,550
I got some bee venom from him.

644
00:35:37,790 --> 00:35:38,270
Just a few minutes.

645
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:47,840
Miss Zhu is really weird.

646
00:35:48,600 --> 00:35:49,790
As if she's possessed.

647
00:35:50,510 --> 00:35:52,640
She does whatever Xiaoli says.

648
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:04,270
Miss Zhu.

649
00:36:05,120 --> 00:36:05,950
What are you doing?

650
00:36:06,270 --> 00:36:07,790
I've designed a new dish.

651
00:36:08,200 --> 00:36:09,080
Bee Soup.

652
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:12,080
I was inspired by the black bee.

653
00:36:13,030 --> 00:36:14,230
Isn't it just wonton?

654
00:36:14,470 --> 00:36:15,510
It's not wonton.

655
00:36:15,710 --> 00:36:17,030
It's much smaller.

656
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:18,880
Doesn't it look like the black bee?

657
00:36:23,080 --> 00:36:23,640
Qing,

658
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:25,790
is it a coincidence

659
00:36:26,360 --> 00:36:27,550
that your sister came at this time?

660
00:36:29,920 --> 00:36:30,360
Here.

661
00:36:31,550 --> 00:36:32,440
Xiaoli, try it.

662
00:36:32,600 --> 00:36:33,470
Thank you, Zhu.

663
00:36:43,640 --> 00:36:44,120
Why...?

664
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:46,230
Why does it taste pungent?

665
00:36:46,990 --> 00:36:47,600
This is

666
00:36:47,710 --> 00:36:49,640
what Miss Zhu has designed.

667
00:36:50,160 --> 00:36:51,400
This pungent taste

668
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:52,510
comes from the black bee's venom.

669
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:56,160
It tastes really fancy.

670
00:36:56,270 --> 00:36:58,400
No wonder diners can't forget it.

671
00:36:58,470 --> 00:36:59,200
Of course.

672
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:00,640
The venom comes from the king bee.

673
00:37:01,200 --> 00:37:02,710
It's certainly the best.

674
00:37:03,030 --> 00:37:03,440
Then...

675
00:37:03,640 --> 00:37:05,400
It must be precious.

676
00:37:05,790 --> 00:37:06,950
I won't say it, then.

677
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:10,440
Xiaoli, what were you about to say?

678
00:37:11,230 --> 00:37:13,080
I wanted to ask you

679
00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:14,230
for some bee venom

680
00:37:14,640 --> 00:37:17,360
to cure the beggars with a rash.

681
00:37:17,750 --> 00:37:19,840
But it's too precious.

682
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:21,680
I'll try something else.

683
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:23,440
When she came out of Miss Zhu's room,

684
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:24,360
I thought it was strange.

685
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:25,990
Now, she wants the bee venom.

686
00:37:26,440 --> 00:37:28,270
Miss Xiaoli, you're so kind.

687
00:37:28,640 --> 00:37:30,440
You even want to help the beggars.

688
00:37:31,160 --> 00:37:32,120
Those beggars

689
00:37:32,120 --> 00:37:33,640
can't even afford food,

690
00:37:33,990 --> 00:37:36,470
let alone see a doctor.

691
00:37:37,030 --> 00:37:38,840
So, I'm thinking

692
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,790
if they can be cured

693
00:37:40,120 --> 00:37:41,680
without spending any money.

694
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:44,080
The bee venom is highly toxic.

695
00:37:44,230 --> 00:37:45,360
Even the slightest lapse

696
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:46,840
may get them killed.

697
00:37:47,270 --> 00:37:48,680
Can it really cure the rash?

698
00:37:49,470 --> 00:37:50,600
Xiaoli is right.

699
00:37:51,360 --> 00:37:53,160
The bee venom is very effective

700
00:37:53,160 --> 00:37:54,270
for all kinds of rash.

701
00:37:54,510 --> 00:37:56,230
Not to mention the black bee's venom.

702
00:37:58,990 --> 00:37:59,750
Then, Miss Zhu,

703
00:37:59,750 --> 00:38:00,790
let's give Miss Xiaoli

704
00:38:00,790 --> 00:38:01,710
a bit more bee venom.

705
00:38:02,550 --> 00:38:05,600
We don't have too much.

706
00:38:05,950 --> 00:38:07,920
And Miss Zhu needs it for the dish.

707
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:10,920
Then, Zhu,

708
00:38:11,030 --> 00:38:12,080
don't be embarrassed.

709
00:38:12,470 --> 00:38:14,360
I'll try something else.

710
00:38:14,550 --> 00:38:15,160
Xiaoli,

711
00:38:15,510 --> 00:38:17,120
you can take the bee venom.

712
00:38:17,470 --> 00:38:18,600
Glad you care for people.

713
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:19,880
Really?

714
00:38:19,880 --> 00:38:20,920
Thank you, Zhu.

715
00:38:21,230 --> 00:38:21,710
Let's go.

716
00:38:29,160 --> 00:38:30,270
You shouldn't have said that much.

717
00:38:57,120 --> 00:38:57,710
Miss Zhu,

718
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,640
why are you up so early?

719
00:39:02,680 --> 00:39:05,640
Demons have been running wild in Wuxia.

720
00:39:06,550 --> 00:39:07,790
On Market Dong,

721
00:39:08,270 --> 00:39:10,640
no demon beasts are sold.

722
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:13,080
Miss Zhu,

723
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:15,200
didn't you promise Mr. Chang
you wouldn't eat demons?

724
00:39:15,600 --> 00:39:16,400
But when he's away,

725
00:39:16,400 --> 00:39:17,440
you want to eat them.

726
00:39:17,790 --> 00:39:19,200
Who said that?

727
00:39:19,470 --> 00:39:21,030
I'll just buy some and watch them.

728
00:39:21,440 --> 00:39:22,310
Miss Zhu,

729
00:39:22,510 --> 00:39:23,920
no demon beasts are sold.

730
00:39:24,160 --> 00:39:25,400
But there are all kinds

731
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:26,510
of mortal ingredients.

732
00:39:26,990 --> 00:39:27,470
Look.

733
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:29,200
The shopkeeper recommended

734
00:39:29,470 --> 00:39:30,990
the matsutake and the agaric.

735
00:39:31,510 --> 00:39:32,840
They're rare, too.

736
00:39:34,750 --> 00:39:36,600
There are ordinary ingredients.

737
00:39:36,950 --> 00:39:38,310
I won't waste

738
00:39:38,640 --> 00:39:40,160
my cooking skills on them.

739
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:49,160
Ladies,

740
00:39:49,400 --> 00:39:50,230
what's going on here?

741
00:39:50,990 --> 00:39:51,840
Miss Xiaoli,

742
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:53,440
Miss Zhu wants to cook.

743
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,750
But now, no demon beasts

744
00:39:55,750 --> 00:39:57,120
are sold on the market.

745
00:39:58,200 --> 00:39:59,840
This is all we could find.

746
00:40:03,310 --> 00:40:05,790
Miss Zhu used to make

747
00:40:05,790 --> 00:40:07,200
very rare dishes.

748
00:40:07,510 --> 00:40:09,120
Now, these ingredients

749
00:40:09,310 --> 00:40:10,680
are really normal.

750
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:14,080
Xiaoli is new here.

751
00:40:14,550 --> 00:40:16,470
But she knows
I'm picky about ingredients.

752
00:40:16,950 --> 00:40:18,080
The two of you

753
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:19,790
only find excuses.

754
00:40:25,750 --> 00:40:26,680
But Zhu,

755
00:40:27,030 --> 00:40:28,310
common people

756
00:40:28,400 --> 00:40:29,950
eat these vegetables.

757
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:32,120
If you can make them

758
00:40:32,270 --> 00:40:33,790
into rare dishes,

759
00:40:34,310 --> 00:40:36,120
won't they prove your great skill?

760
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:38,310
That's right, Miss Zhu.

761
00:40:39,160 --> 00:40:41,950
How about we make a hotpot with them?

762
00:40:42,600 --> 00:40:44,400
In winter, isn't that great

763
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:45,160
to have a hotpot together?

764
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:47,750
Hotpot?

765
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:52,120
Good idea.

766
00:40:53,750 --> 00:40:56,510
How about I make a new dish

767
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:58,230
with them?

768
00:40:59,160 --> 00:41:00,230
Awesome.

769
00:41:00,510 --> 00:41:02,680
The hotpot Miss Zhu makes
will be delicious.

770
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:03,360
Right, Cuiyan?

771
00:41:05,470 --> 00:41:07,360
Can we have the hotpot?

772
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:15,470
All right.

773
00:41:16,270 --> 00:41:18,440
Go out and put up a notice.

774
00:41:18,680 --> 00:41:20,080
Tell people in Wuxia.

775
00:41:20,710 --> 00:41:21,510
In three days,

776
00:41:21,950 --> 00:41:24,160
we'll hold a taste test.

777
00:41:27,710 --> 00:41:29,950
Then, we'll be busy again.

778
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:46,950
The taste test of Tianxiang Restaurant
has started.

779
00:41:46,950 --> 00:41:47,400
Let's go and see.

780
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:48,200
Oh, the taste test.

781
00:41:48,200 --> 00:41:48,510
Come on.

782
00:41:48,680 --> 00:41:49,440
Let's go take a look.

783
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:52,320
[Taste Test]

784
00:41:56,680 --> 00:41:57,510
There she is.

785
00:41:57,680 --> 00:41:58,470
At last.

786
00:41:59,200 --> 00:41:59,920
Everybody,

787
00:42:00,550 --> 00:42:01,880
it's the twelfth month.

788
00:42:02,030 --> 00:42:03,600
And it's really cold.

789
00:42:03,600 --> 00:42:04,600
Miss Zhu

790
00:42:05,120 --> 00:42:07,950
invites all homeless guys in Wuxia

791
00:42:08,030 --> 00:42:09,270
to enter our restaurant first.

792
00:42:16,440 --> 00:42:17,990
Why are they here?

793
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:21,120
Miss Zhu is doing

794
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:22,510
a big act of kindness.

795
00:42:22,600 --> 00:42:23,950
Kindness, indeed.

796
00:42:24,160 --> 00:42:25,710
Miss Zhu is so kind.

797
00:42:25,710 --> 00:42:26,200
Impressive.

798
00:42:26,310 --> 00:42:27,360
She's so nice.

799
00:42:45,270 --> 00:42:45,990
Miss Zhu,

800
00:42:45,990 --> 00:42:47,160
it's really kind of you.

801
00:42:47,160 --> 00:42:48,160
Thank you, Miss Zhu.

802
00:42:48,440 --> 00:42:50,230
Thank you, Miss Zhu.

803
00:42:50,230 --> 00:42:51,310
You're so kind.

804
00:42:51,710 --> 00:42:52,710
Thank you, Miss Zhu.

805
00:42:53,230 --> 00:42:54,200
Thanks, Miss Zhu.

806
00:42:54,200 --> 00:42:54,990
Take your seats.

807
00:43:05,840 --> 00:43:07,400
It's the springwater

808
00:43:07,400 --> 00:43:08,550
from the cliff in Cangwu Mountain

809
00:43:09,030 --> 00:43:10,640
twenty li away from Wuxia.

810
00:43:10,880 --> 00:43:12,120
It was delivered yesterday

811
00:43:12,160 --> 00:43:13,920
and kept in a fresh bamboo vessel.

812
00:43:14,680 --> 00:43:16,600
I need such sweet water

813
00:43:16,600 --> 00:43:18,160
for a great dish.

814
00:43:30,310 --> 00:43:31,230
The Shennong Tripod

815
00:43:31,400 --> 00:43:32,920
is a precious pot.

816
00:43:33,840 --> 00:43:37,030
Mr. Shennong used it
when tasting the herbs.

817
00:43:37,790 --> 00:43:38,950
Common people usually use herbs

818
00:43:38,950 --> 00:43:40,640
as the spice in a hotpot

819
00:43:41,440 --> 00:43:42,790
for more nutrition.

820
00:43:43,470 --> 00:43:44,440
The Shennong Tripod

821
00:43:44,680 --> 00:43:46,950
works better on spleen strengthening.

822
00:44:08,160 --> 00:44:10,360
This is the most tender part of the steak.

823
00:44:10,840 --> 00:44:11,920
The thickness of it

824
00:44:11,920 --> 00:44:13,550
decides how it will taste.

825
00:44:14,270 --> 00:44:15,880
If it's too thick, it won't cook well

826
00:44:15,880 --> 00:44:16,880
and it'll be hard to chew.

827
00:44:17,310 --> 00:44:19,080
If it's too thin, it'll be gone in water

828
00:44:19,080 --> 00:44:20,080
and melt in the mouth.

829
00:44:20,360 --> 00:44:21,160
It won't be tasty.

830
00:45:07,320 --> 00:45:13,050
♪Here's a flower for you♪

831
00:45:13,710 --> 00:45:18,190
♪I don't know what to say
when we look at each other♪

832
00:45:20,040 --> 00:45:25,830
♪Time goes by so quickly♪

833
00:45:26,180 --> 00:45:31,500
♪My obsession leads to my fate♪

834
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:37,840
♪Destiny is confusing over the years♪

835
00:45:38,430 --> 00:45:44,370
♪It feels bleak even with the light on♪

836
00:45:44,710 --> 00:45:47,910
♪I see the shadow
when I almost forget you♪

837
00:45:47,910 --> 00:45:51,270
♪A ray of light on my journey♪

838
00:45:51,270 --> 00:45:57,460
♪It's like you're here
to pour out your heart♪

839
00:45:57,580 --> 00:46:03,600
♪Although the memories of our love
bring us pain♪

840
00:46:04,010 --> 00:46:10,160
♪All I ask for is to hold your hand
until the end of time♪

841
00:46:10,330 --> 00:46:13,480
♪Selflessly♪

842
00:46:13,640 --> 00:46:17,040
♪We taste the sorrows and joys♪

843
00:46:17,510 --> 00:46:24,520
♪I'll never let you go
till death do us part♪
